  "about": "Mushoku Tensei: Jobless Reincarnation is a Japanese anime television series produced by Studio Bind based on the light novel series Mushoku Tensei, written by Rifujin na Magonote and illustrated by Shirotaka. The series is notable for being the primary reason for the formation of Studio Bind, a joint venture between White Fox and Egg Firm, specifically to ensure a high-quality, long-term adaptation of the source material.\nThe series follows a 34-year-old shut-in who dies while saving a teenager and is reincarnated in a world of sword and sorcery as Rudeus Greyrat. Retaining his memories, he resolves to live his new life to the fullest without regrets.",
